    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Dig Deeper</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Descend deep into the earth</strong> as you uncover treasure, trash, and everything in between!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286460/extras/303830d497f4fb99e2cad826d1ed79bb.poster.avif?t=1769017091\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286460/extras/303830d497f4fb99e2cad826d1ed79bb.webm?t=1769017091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286460/extras/303830d497f4fb99e2cad826d1ed79bb.mp4?t=1769017091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Work Together</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Invite <strong>up to 12 friends</strong> then watch teamwork instantly collapse the moment someone throws a bomb at the exit tunnel “by accident.”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286460/extras/9b66972e8628ef8c1b33ca48d0b2c9b2.poster.avif?t=1769017091\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286460/extras/9b66972e8628ef8c1b33ca48d0b2c9b2.webm?t=1769017091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286460/extras/9b66972e8628ef8c1b33ca48d0b2c9b2.mp4?t=1769017091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Unlock Relics and Tools to Carve the Earth</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Find <strong>loads of relics</strong> ranging from “mildly helpful” to “violates several mining laws.” Combine them with ridiculous tools to absolutely obliterate the ground and your debt... Mostly the ground though.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286460/extras/98270ee14b7716b8c8860233e22c19fd.poster.avif?t=1769017091\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286460/extras/98270ee14b7716b8c8860233e22c19fd.webm?t=1769017091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286460/extras/98270ee14b7716b8c8860233e22c19fd.mp4?t=1769017091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Proximity Voice chat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Experience the joy of <strong>yelling at your friends in a hole</strong>. Hear their screams echo through the hole as they drop your debt paying valuables on the ground instead of in the ore bin. Truly immersive. (No we don't know why we added it either)</p>",
